  "lyrics": {
    "v1": "You parents, hear what Jesus taught When little ones to him were brought: Forbid them not, but heed my plea Permitting them to come to me.",
    "v2": "Obey your Lord and let his truth Be taught your children in their youth That they in church and school may dwell And learn their Savior&#39;s praise to tell.",
    "v3": "For if you love them as you ought, To Christ your children will be brought. If thus you place them in his care, All in your family well shall fare."
  },
